BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313303657@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260302T054838Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260302T203000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260302T205000
SUMMARY:Inner Body Meditation (20 minutes)
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\n"Awareness of the inner body takes you bey
 ond the mind." - Eckhart Tolle\n\nIn this mediation session we will bring 
 our attention here: to the inner body. Sessions are suitable for newcomers
 \, those experienced in Tolle's teachings and anyone wishing to remain com
 pletely anonymous. They will last around 20 minutes and cameras and microp
 hones will be disabled.\n(Depending on the situation\, a free discussion m
 ay be held at the end with mics and cameras allowed.)\n\nSee you there!\n\
 nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Katie online mediation group. V
 isit [this Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/) fo
 r more information.\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no memb
 ers have joined after 10 minutes.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313303657/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260211T023645Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260211T023645Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313319443@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260302T054838Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260303T203000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260303T213000
SUMMARY:Awakening Awareness: Embracing This Moment
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nFeel free to join as we get still and prac
 tise presence within this moment. We will discuss and observe the obstacle
 s that\, seemingly\, block us from being present and bring awareness to ou
 r unconsciousness in a safe\, inclusive and affirming way.\n\nSessions are
  suitable for newcomers\, those experienced in Tolle's teaching and anyone
  wishing to remain completely anonymous.\n\nSee you there!\n\nEmrys has be
 en passionate about mindfulness since 2010 and since 2021 he has been orga
 nising free\, weekly online meditation groups. For more information on his
  free Work of Byron Katie online mediation group\, visit [this Meetup Grou
 p link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313319443/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260212T022425Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260212T022425Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313335488@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260302T054838Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260304T203000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260304T213000
SUMMARY:Beginners in The Work of Byron Katie: Newcomers Welcome
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nTo RSVP\, please [click here](https://dash
 board.mailerlite.com/forms/1073947/134679151955150756/share). Guests must 
 complete a contact form and the Zoom link will be sent to by email. Thank 
 you.\n\nA free Zoom meditation session designed with newcomers in mind. Se
 ssions will include at least one hour of facilitation (meditation) and the
 re is room for questions and answers throughout. If you're curious about T
 he Work\, you're invited to join!\n\nSee you there!\n\n**To book a free in
 troductory private session with Emrys\, [click here](https://calendly.com/
 mindfulnesswithemrys/onehoursession)[.](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.busin
 ess.site/)**\n\nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Katie Meetup gro
 up. Visit: [https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree](https://www.meetup.co
 m/thework-runsfree/)\n\n*Find out more about Emrys [here](https://mindfuln
 esswithemrys.business.site/)[.](http://linktr.ee/theworkrunsfree)*\n\nTo b
 est prepare for each session\, complete a *Judge Your Neighbour* worksheet
  free at [https://thework.com/part-three/](https://thework.com/part-three/
 ) or visit [http://www.thework.com](http://www.thework.com)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313335488/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260213T021608Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260213T021608Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
